</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/4MnQi042cgc" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/10/an-alleged-member-of-the-revil-ransomware-gang-has-been-arrested-in-poland/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=an-alleged-member-of-the-revil-ransomware-gang-has-been-arrested-in-poland</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>iPhone SE3 具屏下指紋識別，將搭配 A14 處理器</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/QiRYP1bxmns/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 10 Nov 2021 11:16:19 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPhone SE 3]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1070591</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Apple 早於去年四月發佈 iPhone SE2，而新一代 iPhone SE3 的消息亦不斷增加。據最新消 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 早於去年四月發佈 iPhone SE2，而新一代 iPhone SE3 的消息亦不斷增加。據最新消息透露，Apple 正準備推出新款 iPhone SE，且該設備極有可能採用屏下指紋識別技術。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">據 iPhone SE 3 供應鏈消息，新一代的 iPhone SE 將會採用屏下指紋識別技術，但現時 LCD 屏下指紋技術尚未量產商用，並且其屏下指紋技術體驗不及 OLED 屏幕指紋。若 Apple 在 iPhone SE3 採用了大尺寸的 LCD 屏幕後，其指紋識別模塊將會放到側邊，而一部消息指出 iPhone SE3 可能會像 iPhone XR 那樣使用 Face ID 替代 Touch ID。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">除屏下指紋解鎖外，亦有消息指 iPhone SE3 或將配備與 iPhone 12 系列一樣的 A14 處理器及 5G 網絡制式。但現時 Apple 面臨缺少處理器的問題，因此估計距離 iPhone SE3 正式發佈尚有一段時間。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">有消息稱 iPhone SE3 預計將推出兩個版本，其中低配版售價為 499 美元（約 HK$3890），高配版為 699 美元（約 HK$5460）。如果配備 5G 網絡的 iPhone SE3 一旦面世，將是目前售價最低的 5G iPhone 機型。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2021/10/22/iphone-se-3-feature-xr-design-touch-id-last-lcd/">MacRumors</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=QiRYP1bxmns:q0WMld4yG5I:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=QiRYP1bxmns:q0WMld4yG5I:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/QiRYP1bxmns" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/10/iphone-se-3-rumored-to-feature-iphone-xr-design-with-touch-id/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=iphone-se-3-rumored-to-feature-iphone-xr-design-with-touch-id</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>《Elden Ring》首輪試玩資格公佈，黃牛高價炒賣最高$550</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/Rvtn3FKlYbE/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 10 Nov 2021 11:15:25 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[城中熱話]]></category><category><![CDATA[Elden Ring]]></category><category><![CDATA[艾爾登法環]]></category><category><![CDATA[黃牛]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1070558</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>FromSoftware 開發，BANDAI NAMCO Entertainment 預定 2022 年 2  [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">FromSoftware 開發，BANDAI NAMCO Entertainment 預定 2022 年 2 月 25 日推出的奇幻動作角色扮演遊戲《艾爾登法環》（Elden Ring）日前推出首輪測試抽選，日服昨日公佈了首輪試玩資格的當選結果，但拍賣網上已出現有黃牛炒賣。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1070559" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/52BDE366-C158-4B6D-B159-B19D7362AAAF-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/52BDE366-C158-4B6D-B159-B19D7362AAAF-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/52BDE366-C158-4B6D-B159-B19D7362AAAF-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/52BDE366-C158-4B6D-B159-B19D7362AAAF.jpeg 827w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">《Elden Ring》早前釋出需要抽籤的 Beta 版測試活動，玩家可以通過 PlayStation 或者 Xbox 平台服務參加序號抽取活動。昨日官方公佈日服測試的抽選結果，能夠當選的玩家只有少數。有黃牛就看準商機，將當選資格放到網上炒賣。在「Mercari」、「Yahoo 拍賣」、「PayPayフリマ」等日本的二手拍賣網均出現了《Elden Ring》的當選資格作商品售賣，成交價高達 8000 日圓（約 $552 港幣）。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1070560" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/30BC56FF-CC28-4840-8E40-7F3CADE3C0CA-579x580.jpeg" alt="" width="579" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/30BC56FF-CC28-4840-8E40-7F3CADE3C0CA-579x580.jpeg 579w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/30BC56FF-CC28-4840-8E40-7F3CADE3C0CA-899x900.jpeg 899w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/30BC56FF-CC28-4840-8E40-7F3CADE3C0CA-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/30BC56FF-CC28-4840-8E40-7F3CADE3C0CA-768x769.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/30BC56FF-CC28-4840-8E40-7F3CADE3C0CA.jpeg 1130w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 579px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1070561" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BF859B50-3E58-49E6-A648-1F31DA70890F-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BF859B50-3E58-49E6-A648-1F31DA70890F-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BF859B50-3E58-49E6-A648-1F31DA70890F-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/BF859B50-3E58-49E6-A648-1F31DA70890F.jpeg 1170w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1070562" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/97BCA5A8-C23B-45D2-8391-CD151870AEDC-531x580.jpeg" alt="" width="531" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/97BCA5A8-C23B-45D2-8391-CD151870AEDC-531x580.jpeg 531w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/97BCA5A8-C23B-45D2-8391-CD151870AEDC-824x900.jpeg 824w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/97BCA5A8-C23B-45D2-8391-CD151870AEDC-768x839.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/97BCA5A8-C23B-45D2-8391-CD151870AEDC.jpeg 1153w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 531px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">遊戲官方網站已註明玩家可免費將測試資格轉讓給朋友或是熟人，但不能販賣或轉售測試資格，因此炒賣是官方嚴禁的行為。港台繁中版的抽選結果就在今日公佈。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：</span><a href="https://jp.mercari.com/item/m33601422747"><span style="font-weight: 400;">mercari</span></a></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; </span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
