</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/Rvtn3FKlYbE" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/10/bandai-namco-entertainment-elden-ring/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=bandai-namco-entertainment-elden-ring</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>Uber Taxi 司機反口要計錶，要求乘客多付 $90 惹爭議</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/FyMPMifXBu4/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 10 Nov 2021 11:12:11 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[城中熱話]]></category><category><![CDATA[uber]]></category><category><![CDATA[ubertaxi]]></category><category><![CDATA[的士]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1070714</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Uber 早前推出 Uber Taxi 服務，的士司機也可透過 Uber 接單。但近日就有發生司機完成訂單後， [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Uber 早前推出 Uber Taxi 服務，的士司機也可透過 Uber 接單。但近日就有發生司機完成訂單後，要求客人按錶支付原價車資的事件。有的士司機在 Facebook 發文，稱自己經 Uber Taxi 接單從機場出發前往銅鑼灣，程式收取款項和錶頭車資約有 $90 差額，即要求客人額外支付所需車資，隨即引起熱議。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1070715 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1C52ECB0-BA97-4530-9797-CD85356BD80F-467x580.jpeg" alt="" width="467" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1C52ECB0-BA97-4530-9797-CD85356BD80F-467x580.jpeg 467w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1C52ECB0-BA97-4530-9797-CD85356BD80F-724x900.jpeg 724w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1C52ECB0-BA97-4530-9797-CD85356BD80F-768x955.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1C52ECB0-BA97-4530-9797-CD85356BD80F.jpeg 1016w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 467px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">司機在帖文中提及，「Uber Taxi 和錶頭差價，加回程隧道費，加 2 件行李擺尾箱，相差 90 蚊，叫乘客補回，佢居然畀 100 唔使找」。他更表示，乘客知道他只收到約 200 元後，更指「Uber 食水深，剝削司機」。帖文引起網民熱烈回應，當中有不少留言批評司機的做法，表示司機無視 Uber 分發給他的獎金，更有留言表示「有加乘時你就照收, 少過錶頭時你又要人補返差價, 邊夠你玩呀師兄, 成個行業就你啲人攪衰晒。」</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1070717" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/8A07F717-359E-40B7-BBA2-88F99507BD49-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/8A07F717-359E-40B7-BBA2-88F99507BD49-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/8A07F717-359E-40B7-BBA2-88F99507BD49-675x900.jpeg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/8A07F717-359E-40B7-BBA2-88F99507BD49-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/8A07F717-359E-40B7-BBA2-88F99507BD49-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/8A07F717-359E-40B7-BBA2-88F99507BD49.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1070718" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/7DB174CB-7556-4F5D-B3AA-151D4195326F-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/7DB174CB-7556-4F5D-B3AA-151D4195326F-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/7DB174CB-7556-4F5D-B3AA-151D4195326F-675x900.jpeg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/7DB174CB-7556-4F5D-B3AA-151D4195326F-768x1024.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/7DB174CB-7556-4F5D-B3AA-151D4195326F-1152x1536.jpeg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/7DB174CB-7556-4F5D-B3AA-151D4195326F.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1070716" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/6E288D61-3C3A-45E7-9473-74F1282C701B-694x132.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="132" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/6E288D61-3C3A-45E7-9473-74F1282C701B-694x132.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/6E288D61-3C3A-45E7-9473-74F1282C701B-768x146.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/6E288D61-3C3A-45E7-9473-74F1282C701B.jpeg 1040w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">亦有網民提及，Uber 與部分的士司機以「包車」形式運作，若當時的士由 Uber 包車，再分配不同乘客乘坐，的士就不能按錶收費。據現行法例，的士除可以按錶收費外，亦可以提供預約的包車服務。根據《道路交通 (公共服務車輛) 規例》（第 374D 章）第 38 條，公共服務車輛包括的士可以提供整段時間租用服務，而出租收費金額是基於該車輛被租用的時間（不論是否須就該車出租時所行駛的哩數而另收附加費），或基於與租用人協議的其他條款。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：</span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/1477482755899091/posts/3003806029933415/"><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Facebook</span></a></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
